</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_348" id="173r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_348_r1l14">Den von Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_348_r1l15"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> . wan wır vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehen</expan> . daʒ Jr von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedıgıſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd ʒu Beheım etc künıg vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l17">auch wıe es in dem lande ʒu Beheım 
<add><ab facs="#facs_348_line_1577279040642_2367">yecʒ </ab></add> geſtalt ſey / mer <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l18">meͣre <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemet</expan> vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> mugt / denn wır / So bıtten wır eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l19"><expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gutem <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> daʒ Jr vns bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> / als vıl eẅch denn dauon <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd füklıch ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l21">in guter <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet / vnd ob Jr hernach ıcht treffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l22"> lıchs dauon erfüret vnd gewar wurdet daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr </del> vns 
<del rend="strikethrough">das bey </del> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l23">ſchreıben gebüret daʒ Jr vns das bey eẅr ſelbs <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbet</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l24">Das bottenlon wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> becʒaln <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd beweıſet eẅch in den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_line_1577279060884_2388">ſachen als freẅntlıch als etc / das wellen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l27"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> martinj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_348" id="173r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Eger</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wan wir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sehen</expan>, daz ir von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigisten
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und zu Beheim etc. künig und auch wie es
                        in dem lande zu Beheim <add>yecz</add> gestalt sey, mer
                                <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemet</expan> und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
                        mugt denn wir, so bitten wir ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gutem
                            <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir uns bey
                            <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> als vil ewch denn davon
                                <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und füklich sey in guter
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet; und ob ir hernach icht
                        treffenlichs davon erfüret und gewar wurdet, daz uns zu schreiben gebüret,
                        daz ir uns das bey ewr selbs <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibet</expan>, das bottenlon wir
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beczaln <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und
                        beweiset ewch in den sachen als frewntlich als etc. Das wellen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Martini.</ab>
</div>
